{"tid":181590,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"salyu X 小林武史 live in hong kong","createTime":"2017-03-31T17:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T15:59:39.000Z","uid":5218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"061504c99cbdb7c0e1ce5e1ccb379e635e139ec4","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"我真係發夢都估唔到竟然可以向香港睇到 salyu，上次睇佢係向 2014 年特登飛去東京睇，到呢一刻我腦海好一片空白，好似發緊夢咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg?oh=a28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43&amp;oe=595E7101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43%26oe%3D595E7101&h=7d7a5ee8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2605e7b9fbb2c30528ced500447e1e9ceacf62fc","tid":181590,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我真係發夢都估唔到竟然可以向香港睇到 salyu，上次睇佢係向 2014 年特登飛去東京睇，到呢一刻我腦海好一片空白，好似發緊夢咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg?oh=a28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43&amp;oe=595E7101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43%26oe%3D595E7101&h=7d7a5ee8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港開show, 應該得日本仔入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becea07ba74ac253d559d6f2d16c3bf0a7580732","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"節目詳情<br />\n<br />\n戴著耳機的少年，橫過一片翠綠的草原，耳際響起來自「以太」卻醞釀著抑鬱的音樂 &ndash; 這是不是你的青春輓歌？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n曾經以為只存在於光影世界里虛幻縹緲的聲音， 5月22日假九龍灣國際展貿中心MusicZone，YourMum將為你帶來《青春電幻物語 All About Lily Chou-Chou》神秘歌姬Salyu及電影配樂，著名製作人小林武史的首個香港音樂會。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n2001年日本知名導演岩井俊二在描繪過深情雋永的《情書》、淡然哀愁的《煙花》、靈動魔幻的《燕尾蝶》及潔白純粹的《四月物語》後，帶來了沉鬱殘酷的《青春電幻物語》，透過描述幾個中學生的故事展現當代日本年輕人的各種問題。其中貫穿整個電影的中軸就是虛擬歌手「莉莉周」(Lily Chou-Chou)。而扮演Lily Chou-Chou的Salyu也因此大受歡迎，隨後更推出相關完整專輯《呼吸》，當中《回復する傷》同時被國際知名導演塔倫天奴選用在他的經典電影《Kill Bill 》中，成為了一個世代的重要集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本名鈴木圭子的Salyu，藝名來自法語中的「salut」（即「嗨」的意思），很小的時候就開始學習鋼琴。1998年日本著名音樂製作人小林武史（以負責樂團Mr. Children所有作品的監製與編曲而聞名），因緣際會下聽到了Salyu的歌聲立刻為之動容，邀請她釋演Lily Chou-Chou一角，兩人更一拍即合，展開了長期的合作關係，包括了16張單曲、5張專輯及多場音樂會。 除了小林武史，Salyu 同時與著名音樂人森山直太朗、IImari及渡邊善太郎等合作，當然還有她與涉谷系音樂傳奇人物Cornelius（小山田圭吾）合作的前衛實驗電音計劃 Salyu x Salyu，奇幻的歌聲、天馬行空的音樂讓人一聽難忘。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n清亮的歌聲蘊含痛苦憂鬱的暴烈、鮮甜而帶有血腥味，多少觀眾因為《青春電幻物語》裡，Salyu縹緲奇幻的歌聲而著迷，而生命中有些吉光片羽，錯過了就變成遺憾縈繞心中，例如這個難得的音樂會－和一群抱著相同思緒的觀眾共同回憶那些無以名狀的隱隱作痛；那些不可言喻又讓人沉溺的情緒。門票現正公開發售，不要錯過這千戴難逄的機會。"},{"pid":"9e7414dbc23715c5a9ce86ea568b9f86b8aae2f1","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我真係發夢都估唔到竟然可以向香港睇到 salyu，上次睇佢係向 2014 年特登飛去東京睇，到呢一刻我腦海好一片空白，好似發緊夢咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg?oh=a28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43&amp;oe=595E7101\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F17192315_1249547048448521_3848093763038555281_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da28155834ef53303090b097b1a224f43%26oe%3D595E7101&h=7d7a5ee8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港開show, 應該得日本仔入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係，始終香港唔係太多人識。"},{"pid":"77c84f6baac667f35b18f9964cf3be30f1b489f9","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdefca64b6c5397dbeb889b8d1c4d0222013ac4","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fc35c4bb35f8199b2354fdc9416d8a7f5481ed","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:16:21.000Z","msg":"深夜一推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6ee6affe2e1653429bf6d6736e423a6ef00da6","tid":181590,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"睇過 kill bill vol.1 呢首 soundtracks 應該唔會陌生，但奈何偏偏呢首冇輯落隻 soundtracks 度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hxFwk8qdwgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhxFwk8qdwgw&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=28f372fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hxFwk8qdwgw</a>"},{"pid":"3a8bc5b53833d4b144b7bd0f447f5fbd34960053","tid":181590,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過 kill bill vol.1 呢首 soundtracks 應該唔會陌生，但奈何偏偏呢首冇輯落隻 soundtracks 度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hxFwk8qdwgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhxFwk8qdwgw&d=rLp99s1CaA%